quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Nummah seehadaytut rooci haanak duma dabaanak xer (der) daban kaal tatre, usuk cusaanamay xagar как xagaanah tuh suge kalah."
  76,2,"Diggah nanu seehadaytu lab num kee say numuk yengele daacoytih tiffak kaa ginne kaa naqayyaruh, (mokkorruh) tokkel yaabbeeh yable seehadaytu kaa abne."
  76,3,"Diggah nanu tirtô gitaa kee makô gita kaah baxxaqisneh moomintuy faatita akkee kee korostay yangadde akke yakke immay."
  76,4,"Diggah nanu korosuh, silsilootay ibitte keenik edde debraanaa kee, ogoogay fillittee kee gaboobi ittat keenik edde yaxeenii kee, saqiir deqsitta giráy ken carrisa keenih massosne."
  76,5,"Diggah meqe mari galoosay gocoyuk (kamri) kibuk taniy agleh kaafuur lek yaaquben."
  76,6,"Ama gocoyuy yaaqubeeniy kaafuur agleh edde yani, is daray Yallih naqoosa как taaqube, usun ayfuxxukiyyah tet yayfuxxukeeniih, faxxa heen kabul tet beyan."
  76,7,"Ama mari axbuux (nadri) duudusaah, Qhiyaamah ayróy umaané как fixiixih tani Yallih digaalák meesitan."
  76,8,"Kaadu usun tumaliiy qayxixxuu kee seewaytu maaqó yaskamen tet kacanu luk."
  76,9,"Cagalah nanu sin kah naskamem Yallih foocih taaga, galtoo kee faatit siinik elle mafanna iyyan."
  76,10,"Diggah nanu ninni Rabbik meesitna, gibdah fooci edde ribbiima (kamadima) ayrók (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)."
  76,11,"Tokkel Yalli woo ayróh umaanék ken reebiseeh, fooci ifuu kee wallé (farcat) keenih yecee."
  76,12,"Kaadu yisbireenimih sabbatah jannat kee cariiril ken gälte."
  76,13,"Kay addal qaraakiyil kelitak, ayró mayablaanaay, kaxxa xabca mayablan."
  76,14,"Kaadu Kay cooxih silaalo keenit xayyowtah ken silaalisak, kaadu ama cooxih mexexih mafaala xabbacoowiyyah keenih xabbacowta."
  76,15,"Kaadu jannatti urruy ken yakdumc keenit meekisah, mingiilay lakqok tanii kee kobboyyaayiy bililleelak (karaarit kinnuk) tani."
  76,16,"Bililleelay lakqok taniy usun elle faxaanah gidel kiyaasiyyah kiyaaseeni."
  76,17,"Kaadu kay addal galoosay gocoyuk kibuk taniy agleh zanjabiil lek ken yafqen."
  76,18,"Kay addal tan daray, salsabiil deqsittak yaaquben."
  76,19,"Kaadu jannatti urruy elle yanin caalatal elle waara keenit meekita, ken table waqdi luuluy fixiixiseeni ken takka Íe."
  76,20,"Kaadu jannatak faxe ikkeey wagittay, tokkel niqmatay weeloysoonu duude waanaa kee kaxxa Reeda table."
  76,21,"Anxaxin saray xabcin cariirik yanii kee gibdi cariirik yan sari ken xagaral yaniih, qado lakqok tan gabâ biriitat (cagooluk) billiiman, kaadu ken Rabbi yaaqubeenimiy saytuniy taahirik tanik ken yafqe."
  76,22,"Diggah ta galtó sin meqe taamoomih galto kinniih, sin taamoomi addunyal yalli raabiteeh yikcineh yan taamak sugte keenik iyyan."
  76,23,"Diggah Nabiyow Qhuraan oobisiyyah nanu ninnih koi oobisne."
  76,24,"Nabiyow Ku Rabbih meklal isbiraay, korosuk dambit kaxaxah yan marih yab moggolinaay hinnay koroosannuu kee maxqawitit caddok tatreh yan marih yab moggolin."
  76,25,"Kaadu ku Rabbih migaq Carraay, saaku xag."
  76,26,"Kaadu barak tut kaah kummaataay, barak xer waktit salat kaah ab."
  76,27,"Diggah tama mari (koros kinnuk) sissik tiya (addunya kinnuk) kicnoonuuh, qilsi ayroy ellccabol ken qambalta cabaanah (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)."
  76,28,"Nanu ken ginneeh gino keenik karriqqi hayne, kaadu nanu bayisnam fannek, bayissi ken hayneh ken innah yan maray kayrih keenik yayse ciggiilisiyyah ciggiilisenno."
  76,29,"Diggah tama suurá seehadah kassiisi, toysa isi nafsih maqaané faxe num, isi Rabbih gita yabbixe, iimaan kee meqe taamâl."
  76,30,"isin caagiidak hcbeltö caagidiy faxxaana manton, Yalli faxeh akke waytek, diggah Yalli isi ginö caaloota yaaxigi, abba haamal naggaar kinni."
  76,31,"Yalli isi naqoosak isih faxe тага isi Racmat (jannat kinnuk) çulsa, kaadu daalimiinih (koros kinnuk) akeeral qansarissa digaalá massoyse."
